{"tid":1384685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］飲食業都可以幫手罷工㗎，快啲同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:13:16.000Z","uid":257625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"feff6c78637f857069430e60986042875b8dac5c","tid":1384685,"uid":257625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"飲食業要完全罷工唔做嘢就真係難嘅<br />\n但係我哋可以跟着返公司規矩做嘢喎<br />\n務求為客人帶來賓至如歸嘅服務體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以麥叔叔為例<br />\n各位員工，記住要跟着公司規矩做嘢呀<br />\n當客人進入店舖時我哋要大叫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">歡迎光臨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跟住就係各個崗位要做嘅內容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位點膳服務員</span></span><br />\n當有客人嚟嗰陣時我哋要講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">歡迎光臨，有咩想食</span></span><br />\n記住呀，點膳嘅時候我哋要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">小心啲慢慢嚟</span></span><br />\n費事一陣間要改單啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順帶一提改單嘅時候我哋記得要通知經理啊<br />\n當客人就快點完餐嘅時候<br />\n我哋要記得推薦額外點膳比客人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">加多$10有兩件雞翼喎，請問你需唔需要</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得客人完成點膳嗰陣時<br />\n我哋要大叫<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝晒下次再嚟啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會睇小點膳時間，當每一個人用2分鐘點餐<br />\n後面就會塞晒成堆人喺度㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">集合點膳服務員</span></span>（即係執嘢食嗰個）<br />\n我哋記住要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逐樣檢查</span></span>係咪所有嘢都齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有產品唔符合公司規格<br />\n即係嗰啲<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔夠熱，唔夠新鮮</span></span>嗰啲呢，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住叫廚房重新再做過啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廚房嘅各位</span></span><br />\n記得我哋要製造一啲符合公司規格產品<br />\n每一樣野我哋都要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即時整出嚟</span></span><br />\n務求令到顧客有最優質的食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點膳呈上員</span></span></span><br />\n記得我哋再要核對多次，顧客點膳係唔係齊全<br />\n如果又有唔合規格嘅記得要換左佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有客人問點解我個餐咁耐都未到？<br />\n可以答佢<br />\n［red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為咗提供最優質嘅食物比客人，我哋所有食物都係即時製造，所以要花較長時間，要你等咁耐真係唔好意思</span>[/red]<br />\n如果有人問你攞飲管，你可以咁樣答佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思啊，公司為咗支持環保，依家我哋唔會主動提供飲管㗎啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有各位經理</span></span><br />\n我知道要你哋咁就會承受好大風險<br />\n但係希望你地會幫手啦<br />\n記住公司嘅宗旨啊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為顧客提供最優質食物</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小呢啲步驟啊<br />\n我哋做齊晒嘅話，15分鐘之內應該都攞唔到餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係最重要嘅都係買嘅人，唔好催我哋啦，都唔好投訴我哋<br />\n如果唔係嘅話其實我哋唔夠膽咁樣做㗎<br />\n公司要我地追時間啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然最好落單嗰陣時可以同我地講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慢慢嚟唔使急，最緊要啲嘢係要即整</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有呀，如果有客屌我哋嗰陣時<br />\n希望各位可以幫幫手，如果唔係我哋真係好難做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位幫手推到全部做飲食業嘅都睇到呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"504cec35b5680c2112d6ff7016118c0082c0701b","tid":1384685,"uid":257625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:42:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"18448632ca629d6d0e2710559544b9ffb975ae6b","tid":1384685,"uid":257625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb4217555e48954c9387ca85397d9992cf11ebe8","tid":1384685,"uid":80164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"講起麥當勞，我諗起某日去買野食，見到有個客人行去麥當勞櫃檯問員工要膠袋，個員工就同佢講膠袋要比5毫子<br />\n個客人就好嬲，鬧個員工你唔比膠袋我我點拎番屋企<br />\n之後個員工答佢，係囉，最衰都係政府啦，無啦啦收咩膠袋稅<br />\n然後個客就死死氣走咗<br />\n唔知之後個客會唔會寫信去政府部門投訴膠袋稅擾民，我好好奇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9092e3c19236a383bc60676e94bd0137e9d843d","tid":1384685,"uid":16228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}